The impact of the asteroid mine had caused a strong tremor through all the 
northwestern america. By the time the quake reached the chivtron base, 
Starstomp was getting on the verge of getting to stasis lock. She needed 
help and fast. Since she was not used to her beast mode, she transformed and 
tried to see the status of the CR chamber. It was no use, though, because it 
was totally out of function for regenerative uses. Again she needed help and 
she needed it so slaggin fast!!!

Starstomp:
I am the cybertronian named Starstomp and I request urgent assistance. To 
any sentient entities that are situated to the west of my position, please 
comply as fast as possible. I am currently bordering stasis lock and I am 
completely willing to help you!! Please assist!!!
